B.T4=new A.Gt("# Privacy Policy\n\nYour privacy is our priority. This app is designed to process your data locally. We do not collect, store, or transmit any personal information to our own servers.\n\n## 1. Health and Sensor Data\n\nThe app requests access to your heart rate sensor via Bluetooth, as well as the gyroscope, accelerometer, motion, GPS to monitor workout intensity. All sensor data is processed strictly on-device in real-time. We do not store or upload your health or fitness metrics.\n\n## 2. Location Data\n\nTo enable the GPS running mode, the app requires access to your location. This data is never sent to our servers. Your device uses an internet connection solely to communicate your location to Apple Maps on iOS or OpenStreetMap on other platforms to render the map interface.\n\n## 3. Local Storage\n\nYour settings, workouts and workout history are saved entirely on your device's local storage. You maintain full control over this data and can clear it at any time via the app's settings.\n\n## 4. Third-Party Services\n\nThe only external services utilized are Apple Maps on iOS and OpenStreetMap on other platforms for map display. We do not use third-party analytics or advertising trackers.\n\n## Contact\n\nIf you have any questions or concerns about this policy, please contact us at: razvit.timer@proton.me\n",!1,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,B.xg,B.xh,!0,B.xm,!1,null)
